To reset your password click the link below:

<%= edit_password_reset_url(@user.reset_token, email: @user.email) %>

This link will expire in two hours. If you do not reset your password in that time you will have to restart the process.

If you did not request your password to be reset, please ignore this email and your password will stay as it is. 
If you encounter any problems resetting your password please fill out the help ticket form below for us to further assist you. 

